# Day 3 - Installing BLAST+ on WSL2

## Goal
Install BLAST+ locally using Conda and create a FASTA file.

## Commands Used

```bash
conda install -c bioconda blast -y
blastp -version
mkdir ~/blast_practice && cd ~/blast_practice
echo ">mystery\nMTEYKLVVVGAGGVGKSALTIQLIQNHFVDE" > mystery.fasta
cat mystery.fasta
